abstract: David Allen reviews performance by Emerson String Quartet at Alice Tully Hall.
lead_paragraph: On Tuesday, at Alice Tully Hall, the group wrapped up a season that one of the Chamber Music Society of Lincoln Center’s leaders billed as record-setting.
